%%{init: {'theme': 'forest'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor FW as Firmware
  participant API as Go API

  FW->>API: GET /api/bootstrap?imei=...\n(header x-api-key)
  API-->>FW: 200 JSON bootstrap\n(optional) govt_broker

  alt Govt broker configured
    FW->>FW: Connect to govt_broker.endpoints[0]\nusing govt credentials
    FW->>FW: Publish/subscribe on govt topics as required
  else Not configured
    FW->>FW: Skip govt broker logic
  end
